data.name: PRE-FILLED SYRINGES
data.description:
## COMPOSITION
- Barrel + Plunger: Medical Grade Polypropylene (PP)
- Gasket: Isoprene Latex-Free Rubber and Natural Rubber

## STERILIZATION
- Ethylene Oxide (EO) Sterile

## PRESENTATIONS
- Luer Slip Tips with Cap
- Latex-free Gasket
- Colour coded caps
- Customizable graduation including logo
- Concentric Luer Tips

## PERFORMANCE
- Easy to use
- Clear graduation printing technology
- High Transparency Barrel
- Smooth sliding
